snippet.textDisplay:
Dear amplitude (his funny nickname) (someone i met in highschool)
 Whenever i listen to ts beautiful song i remember the time when i fell in love with you you were staring at me in the corridor i was walking past by you ,hurry to give my maths exam. I saw those eyes looking at me and my heartbeat was so high that i could listen to my heartbeat through my chest after class 10th i had to change my school,thinking about I'll never get to see you walking or doing chaukidari on corridor 😂 or staring at random students i was really sad you were very dear to me even though you didn't like me i loved you unconditionally even though when you called me weirdo but the end of the day i was js a lovestruck teenager. I hope sometimes that i haven't met you or i wish you had never joined my old School but sometimes i think about those beautiful times when i used to find pretences to see you. You gave me the most vulnerable and loveliest moments of my life you made me to love you unconditionally.but here I'm in my new school thinking I'll never meet you again corrodes me inside.i hope you listen to ts song and find my comment
